Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是真正的海龍神社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龍大人就在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  鑰匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)\fn方正隶二_GBK\an5\fs45}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N飛出  藍蘭島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積滿了苔蘚很滑  要小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:00:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龍大人是怎樣的神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為到現在為止誰都沒有見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的主人們所保護的神究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  和行人在一起就沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海龍大人的叫聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫聲停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龍大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龍大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的願望是傳達不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因就是…海龍大人會先聽取我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是海龍大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龍大人  請務必實現我的願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  還帶了供奉用的紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好這裡有根繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬍子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龍大人  請保佑行人能離開這島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是鬍子  大概是海龍大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知情的情況下好像不小心拉斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像拉斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  居然把海龍大人的鬍子給拽下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太讓人吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會受到天罰的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是因為你們太沒用了我才去阻礙他們祈願的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是失敗了偶然中拽下來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這樣一來  海龍大人也不會保佑行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  也只能放棄離開島了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看吧  這樣一來行人就屬於我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會變成綾音的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個和那個是兩回事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會承認的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終女婿大人會選擇你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的喜歡他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是應該考慮究竟如何做才為女婿大人好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼對行人來說是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人正準備出海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人能觀察到遠處的式神所看到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是送你到中途吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有海龍大人的保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能帶小鈴去那麼危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一起去的話才會擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就該保護女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來這島上的時候確實什麼都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在已經變得很可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不得不去救美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣  也不能讓小鈴深處險境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人也沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  女婿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓行人走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你真的覺得這樣做可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有…這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是女婿大人所盼望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算失去生命也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生魚片…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生魚片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  快去追行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到漩渦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能越過那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真笨  明明不可能有這種事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道不該這樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:08:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我不要與行人永別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  快回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生魚片  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
