Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龍大人生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼說都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不過沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生魚片  去海龍大人所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算從海面上過去嗎
